            "type": "text",
            "text": "Linear PI is a one-line change and works well enough for 4–8× context extension with a small fine-tuning budget. For 32–128× extension (e.g. GPT-4-level 128k contexts), NTK or YaRN with their improved handling of high-frequency dimensions is necessary."
          }
